te the\r\n> two options\r\n> Doing the delay may be trickier, but I'll give a try.\r\n>\r\n> \8212\r\n> Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub<https://github.com/rethinkdb/rethinkdb/issues/584#issuecomment-15820513>\r\n> .\r\n>"
